==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Recording
<hw>Re*cord"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Keeping a record or a register;
<as>as, a <ex>recording</ex> secretary</as>; -- applied to numerous
instruments with an automatic appliance which makes a record of their
action; <as>as, a <ex>recording</ex> gauge or telegraph</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

